name: GigaChad Generator
description:
A true GymBro is always willing to help his fellow comrades on their journey to success.

Now, thanks to GigaChad Generator, you can put yourself in the shoes of an authentic GigaChad and assist your homies on their routines, while letting them know the danger behind evil vending machines.

Download GigaChad Generator and build your very own GigaGym!

LaggedHeads - Albert Gómez, Rubén Maillo, Martí Parladé, Mikel Quereda, Martí Serras

This game uses some non-copyrighted music and sounds, as well as some videos that don't belong to us. The rest of the assets have been created from scratch by the team.
